title: Swamp Python
body:
Swamp Python

Unlike the trees of the grassy plain, the trees In the forest were very big and thick.

Because of the dense trees, very little sunlight was able to enter the forest. But Evan had no problem seeing even in the dark.

The ground of the forest was muddy and was filled with water, that resembles a swamp. The water level of the ground was around twenty centimeters.

Splash -!

The sound of water splashing rang out as Evan moved forward. His senses were on full alert, and he was paying great attention to the water around him.

'There must be some monsters in this shallow muddy water' Evan thought while moving forward.
